Tailoring the Build Settings
----------------------------

* see toplevel README


Basic Usage
----------------------------

For the TI Launchpad, connect the USB-port to your PC. Then connect to the MCU through serial line by using the following parameters: 

* serial port (e.g. /dev/ttyACM0 on Linux)
* 9600 bauds
* 8 databits
* 1 stopbits

